 "I will pay, and in doing so, I will pay for your sins.

986
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:02,000
 "I will pay the debt that you deserve to pay.

987
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:05,000
 "I will die the death that you deserve to die.

988
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:07,000
 "I'll live the life you cannot live,

989
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:10,000
 "and if you will just by faith

990
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:13,000
 "accept that Jesus paid for my sin,

991
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:16,000
 "you will live forever, and you will say,

992
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:19,000
 "with all the saints for eternity, we win.

993
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:21,000
 "And no matter what happens, we win.

994
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:23,000
 "No matter what we face, we win.

995
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,000
 "Neither death, life, nor anything else

996
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:28,000
 "in all creation, tribulation, famine, distress,"

997
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:30,000
 as Romans 8 says, "can separate us from Christ.

998
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:33,000
 "We win, and we exhale now,

999
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:37,000
 "knowing that you are the God who comes through,

1000
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:41,000
 "because you already have, and you will come again,

1001
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:46,000
 "and you've already paid, and through you, we win."

