 If you don't know that God, I'm gonna pray that you would.

1003
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:50,000
 We'd love to talk to you about it.

1004
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,000
 That's why we do everything that you see here.

1005
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:55,000
 That's why every psalm was written.

1006
00:44:55,000 --> 00:44:59,000
 That's why all of life, all of your life exists.

1007
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,000
 That's the meaning for which you were born.

1008
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:03,000
 I'm gonna pray that you would.

1009
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:04,000
 Father, thank you for the psalms.

