00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:06,000
 Thank you for the writings

1012
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:13,000
 of just men who loved you, and who knew you,

1013
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:15,000
 and who through their writings,

1014
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:17,000
 we are able to know you better.

1015
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,000
 Thank you.

1016
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:20,000
 God, thank you for Jesus.

1017
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,000
 Thank you for Jesus.

1018
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:24,000
 Thank you for the Passover lamb,

1019
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:27,000
 the true one whose blood was shed

1020
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:29,000
 so that mine would not have to be.

