00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:34,000
 And who did so not because of a reluctance or an obligation,

1022
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:36,000
 because he really loves us.

1023
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:42,000
 You love us with a love that for your people never stops,

1024
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:48,000
 and provides a protection that never fails,

1025
00:45:48,000 --> 00:45:53,000
 and through which we can have confidence to say,

1026
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:58,000
 "We win, no matter what comes my way."

1027
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:01,000
 "What comes my way, and I don't know what that will be, Lord."

